subject: Snowboarding
lead_paragraph: The Olympic gold medalist Shaun White won the snowboard slope-style competition, and Spencer O’Brien of Canada took the women’s event in the first stop on the inaugural Winter Dew Tour in Breckenridge, Colo. White, 22, from Carlsbad, Calif., scored 95.17 points on his second run.
